    	<div class="comment_content">
    		<p>I couldn&#8217;t agree more that there are no universal rules. I just think that in the wide range of leaders and leadership styles, Steve Jobs is an extreme outlier. We&#8217;re all lucky for that, but it makes him even less of a broadly useful role model than most leaders. Thanks.</p>

    	</div>
    	
		    
